* [sol1-Python3]

```Python
class Solution:
    def findContentChildren(self, g: List[int], s: List[int]) -> int:
        g.sort()
        s.sort()
        m, n = len(g), len(s)
        i = j = count = 0

        while i < m and j < n:
            while j < n and g[i] > s[j]:
                j += 1
            if j < n:
                count += 1
            i += 1
            j += 1
        
        return count
```

